lead_paragraph: Everton, Atletico Madrid, Villarreal, Hamburger SV and FC Basel won yesterday to advance to the UEFA Cup’s Round of 32. Everton became the first English club to advance past the group stage when Tim Cahill scored in the 85th minute for a 1-0 victory over Zenit St. Petersburg.
